    Add option to hide incompatible families

    Introduces a new user setting to control whether model families with no compatible models are shown in the catalog. The setting defaults to true (show all families) to maintain current behavior.

    Changes:
    - Add "Show incompatible families" toggle in settings view with explanatory caption
    - Add UserSettings.showIncompatibleFamilies property that persists preference and posts notification on change
    - Skip rendering family headers in MenuController when no valid models exist and setting is disabled
