Author: Emanuil Rusev <hello@erusev.com>
Date:   Fri Nov 21 14:33:42 2025 +0200

    Remove premature caching in MemoryCalculator

    The compatibility check and usable context caching system was optimizing for a scenario (expensive repeated calculations) that doesn't happen in practice. Model catalogs are small, calculations are simple arithmetic, and these functions aren't called in tight loops. This adds ~50 lines of infrastructure with no measurable benefit.

    Also removed a redundant comment in CatalogModelItemView explaining obvious behavior.
